Diamond::

She turned the corner and saw the doorway to the bridge. She looked 
down the hall and wondered if the ship entrance was close by.  She 
took a deep breath and bolted past the bridge and down the hallway.  
She just hoped that she would find the base entrance and be able to 
get out.
